## UX/UI Design System - Comprehensive Implementation

### Product Grid System (MANDATORY)

**ALWAYS implement product grids with these exact specifications:**

```css
/* Responsive Product Grid - REQUIRED for ALL pages */
.products-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--espacamento-lg);
  padding: var(--espacamento-md);
}

/* Mobile: 2 products per row */
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .products-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--espacamento-md);
  }
}

/* Tablet: 3 products per row */
@media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1023px) {
  .products-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--espacamento-lg);
  }
}

/* Desktop: 4 products per row */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .products-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--espacamento-xl);
  }
}
```

